"content": "<style>\nh1.thlex-title { font-size: 1.3em; margin: 0 0 0.4em; }\n.thlex-key { color: #888; font-size: 0.85em; font-weight: normal; margin-right: 0.4em; }\nnav.thlex-index { margin: 0.5em 0 0.75em; }\nnav.thlex-index ul { margin: 0; padding-left: 1.2em; }\nnav.thlex-index li { margin: 0.15em 0; font-size: 0.95em; }\n.thlex-section { margin: 0.6em 0; }\nh2.thlex-heading { font-size: 1em; margin: 0.5em 0 0.2em; }\nh3.thlex-subheading { font-size: 0.95em; font-weight: normal; font-style: italic; margin: 0.2em 0; }\n.thlex-language-sets { margin: 0.3em 0 0.3em 1em; }\n.thlex-language-set { margin: 0.4em 0; padding-left: 0.75em; border-left: 3px solid #e0e0e0; }\n.thlex-language { font-size: 0.8em; color: #888; margin-right: 0.4em; }\n.thlex-lemma { font-weight: bold; font-family: serif; }\n.thlex-translit { color: #555; font-style: italic; font-size: 0.9em; margin-left: 0.3em; }\n.thlex-refs { font-size: 0.85em; color: #444; margin-top: 0.15em; }\n.thlex-paragraphs p { margin: 0.35em 0; font-size: 0.95em; line-height: 1.5; }\n.thlex-image { margin: 0.5em 0; display: block; }\n.thlex-image img { max-width: 100%; height: auto; display: block; }\nfigcaption.thlex-caption { font-size: 0.85em; color: #555; font-style: italic; margin-top: 0.2em; }\n.thlex-abbr { border-bottom: 1px dotted #888; cursor: help; }\n.thlex-xref { color: #1a5fb4; }\nspan[data-bnType=\"bibleReference\"] { color: #1a5fb4; }\ntable.thlex-table { border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 0.9em; margin: 0.5em 0; }\ntable.thlex-table td { padding: 0.2em 0.6em; vertical-align: top; border: 1px solid #ddd; }\ntable.thlex-table tr:first-child td { font-weight: bold; background: #f5f5f5; }\nul.thlex-index-list { margin: 0.4em 0; padding-left: 1.4em; font-size: 0.95em; line-height: 1.6; }\nul.thlex-index-list ul { margin: 0.1em 0; padding-left: 1.4em; }\n.thlex-index-key { font-weight: bold; font-style: italic; }\n</style><h1 class=\"thlex-title\" id=\"REALIA:1.4.2\"><span class=\"thlex-key\">1.4.2</span> 標題：網、網羅（net）</h1><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">經文出處</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-sets\">\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">來： חֵרֶם</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： cherem)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl7:26\">ECC 7:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic7:2\">MIC 7:2</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">來： מִכְמָר</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： mikmar)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa51:20\">ISA 51:20</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">來： מָצוֹד</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： matsod（參)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl7:26\">ECC 7:26</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">來： מְצוּדָה</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： mtsudah)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps66:11\">PSA 66:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek12:13\">EZK 12:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek17:20\">EZK 17:20</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">來： רֶשֶׁת</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： resheth)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job18:8\">JOB 18:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps9:16\">PSA 9:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps10:9\">PSA 10:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps25:15\">PSA 25:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps31:5\">PSA 31:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps35:7\">PSA 35:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps35:8\">PSA 35:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps57:7\">PSA 57:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps140:6\">PSA 140:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov1:17\">PRO 1:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov29:5\">PRO 29:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lam1:13\">LAM 1:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek12:13\">EZK 12:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek17:20\">EZK 17:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek19:8\">EZK 19:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos5:1\">HOS 5:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos7:12\">HOS 7:12</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希： παγίς</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： pagis)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke21:35\">LUK 21:35</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom11:9\">ROM 11:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim3:7\">1TI 3:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim6:9\">1TI 6:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim2:26\">2TI 2:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Tob14:10\">TOB 14:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Tob14:10\">TOB 14:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Wis14:11\">WIS 14:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Sir9:3\">SIR 9:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Sir9:13\">SIR 9:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Sir27:20\">SIR 27:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Sir27:26\">SIR 27:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Sir27:29\">SIR 27:29</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Sir51:2\">SIR 51:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Macc1:35\">1MA 1:35</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Macc5:4\">1MA 5:4</a></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">描述</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>\n            <figure class=\"thlex-image\"><img class=\"thlex-img\" src=\"images/WEB-0339_hunting_net.jpg\" alt=\"男子用網捕鹿（亞述巴尼拔（Ashurbanipal）王狩獵獅子的浮雕，尼尼微北宮，S室，第17-18號壁板，約公元前645-635年）\"><figcaption class=\"thlex-caption\">男子用網捕鹿（亞述巴尼拔（Ashurbanipal）王狩獵獅子的浮雕，尼尼微北宮，S室，第17–18號壁板，約公元前645–635年） (© Zunkir, CC BY-SA 4.0, via Wikimedia Commons)</figcaption></figure>網是用繩子做成的網狀物，或者是帶有很大孔眼的軟織物。</p>\n<hr/>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">用途</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>網是一種狩獵工具，放置在鳥類或野獸可能會飛入或進入的地方，以將其捉獲。網也常用來狩獵，例如，獵人會悄悄跟踪獵物，當足夠接近時，就突然把網扔到獵物身上。</p>\n<hr/>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">翻譯</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>世界各地的人都會使用陷阱來捕捉鳥類或野獸，因此找到一個合適的詞語應該不難。然而，在許多語境中，翻譯者無法確定經文提到的網是用來捕捉野獸，還是用來捕捉鳥類。如果目標語言不作區分，那麼可以使用「網」這個統稱。如果必須要進行區分，翻譯者應仔細考察上下文。下述清單列出了哪些經文是指捕捉野獸（包括人類）的網，哪些經文是指捕捉鳥類的網，哪些經文並未清楚表達：</p>\n<p>野獸：<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps9:16\">PSA 9:16</a> （《和》9:15），<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps35:7\">PSA 35:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps35:8\">PSA 35:8</a> ；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov29:5\">PRO 29:5</a> ；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa51:20\">ISA 51:20</a> ；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lam1:13\">LAM 1:13</a> ；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek12:13\">EZK 12:13</a> ，<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek17:20\">EZK 17:20</a> ，<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek19:8\">EZK 19:8</a> ；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim3:7\">1TI 3:7</a> ；（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Sir9:13\">SIR 9:13</a> ，<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Sir27:20\">SIR 27:20</a> ，<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Sir27:26\">SIR 27:26</a> ，<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Sir27:29\">SIR 27:29</a> ；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Macc1:35\">1MA 1:35</a> ，<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Macc5:4\">1MA 5:4</a> ）</p>\n<p>鳥類：<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov1:17\">PRO 1:17</a> ；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos7:12\">HOS 7:12</a></p>\n<p>不確定：<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job18:8\">JOB 18:8</a> ；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps10:9\">PSA 10:9</a> ，<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps25:15\">PSA 25:15</a> ，<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps31:5\">PSA 31:5</a> （《和》31:4），<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps57:7\">PSA 57:7</a> （《和》57:6），<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps140:6\">PSA 140:6</a> （《和》140:5）；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl7:26\">ECC 7:26</a> ；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos5:1\">HOS 5:1</a> ；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke21:35\">LUK 21:35</a> ；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom11:9\">ROM 11:9</a> ；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim6:9\">1TI 6:9</a> ；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim2:26\">2TI 2:26</a> ；（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Tob14:10\">TOB 14:10</a> ；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Wis14:11\">WIS 14:11</a> ；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Sir9:3\">SIR 9:3</a> ，<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Sir51:2\">SIR 51:2</a> ）</p>\n<p>在<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke21:35\">LUK 21:35</a> ，重點是事件出人意料地發生，而不在於實際的物品；然而，這個物品通常還是會保留在譯文中。</p>\n<p>如果經文是比喻性的，那麼也可以不使用網的比喻，特別是在提到網反而會誤導讀者的情況下；例如，<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic7:2\">MIC 7:2</a> d可以譯作，「每個人都試圖誘捕其他人」（<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"New Century Version\">NCV</abbr> ）。</p>\n</div>\n</div>",
